Umukobwa witwa Nora

Uyu ni umukobwa witwa Nora. Igipupe cye cyitwa Sela.

Nora akunda igipupe cye cyane. Nora akina na Sela buri munsi. Buri joro aryamana n'igipupe cye.

Umunsi umwe, Nora ntiyashoboye kubona igipupe cye. Yarebye hose, ariko ntiyabona Sela. Nora yagize ubwoba bwinshi.

Norah ntabwo yari azi ko nyina yajyanye Sela kumesa. Yamanitse cya igipupe hanze kugirango yumuke.

Nora ati: "Sindi kubona igipupe cyanjye." Nyina ati: "Ntugire ubwoba."

Kuri uwo mugoroba, nyina wa Nora yahaye Nora igipupe. Igipupe cyari gifite isuku cyane. Sela yasaga nkigipupe gishya!

Nora yarishimye cyane. Arasimbuka. Yarabyinnye. Araseka cyane.

Yashimiye nyina.
